<p>Looking north-east, one can see St Paulâ€™s on the left. Some key tall buildings in the middle include 22 Bishopgate, 122 Leadenhall (Cheesgrater), The Scalpel and 20 Fenchurch St (Walkie Talkie). On the right, the tallest building the the Shard, which is the tallest building in the EU.</p>

